ke":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"槍係假<br />\n<br />\n中槍既人反應都係假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be49bd9fa4977f3966c2dcfd2fe4e940f87440c","tid":771434,"uid":35347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d2da0a588bf89db43f3cc9e5ee2e60c2d9bbbe4d","tid":771434,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65eacee77778296e1aea11bfd01c0cb4f7372841","tid":771434,"uid":42042,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T05:00:47.000Z","msg":"反正大家都冇SOURCE,都係CONTENT FARM<br />\n<br />\n我啱啱GOOGLE咗<br />\n<br />\n我自己就唔太信喇<br />\n<br />\n&quot;<br />\n她說：「7月30日下午4點40左右，我在安檢室內遭遇不明武器的襲擊。突然倒在旁邊的沙發上。這個不明武器是什麼呢，我們在網上查了一下，它就叫「遠程電擊防爆器」，這種武器能在五米內將人擊倒，擊中要害，三秒內致人死亡」。<br />\n<br />\n范燕瓊的女兒林靜怡接受自由亞洲電台採訪時稱，前一天，她母親剛做了開顱手術，手術順利，但有十天危險期。醫院又指范燕瓊患血管瘤：「叫什麼血管瘤，但是那一天發生這個事情時監控也看不到，法院那邊也沒有提供。我母親當時說，感覺有五個人拿著什麼東西對她照了一下，就非常難受。她現在不能講話」。<br />\n<br />\n林靜怡說，當時在場的有一名孩子，當晚回家也出現頭痛頭暈等症狀。記者無非確認范燕瓊所受到的襲擊究竟是何種因素所致。但所謂激光槍確實存在，中共反恐武裝部隊已有此裝備。<br />\n&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/8/7/n10622319.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F8%2F7%2Fn10622319.htm&d=Gwu7UGslcp1keCAvSO4gUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=212d52c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/8/7/n10622319.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;<br />\n開發公司公佈這段錄影，是為了回應外媒對ZKZM-500激光槍效力的質疑。TechCrunch資訊科技網評論稱，這類技術至今仍存在科幻小說中，因為靠鋰電池驅動的激光槍不可能產生近距離直射所需的熱能，更別說是射程800米了，而且關鍵在於，激光行進時會分散，距離愈遠，威力就愈弱。<br />\n<br />\nTechCrunch認為，中共散佈該消息的目的是在反對中共政府的異見者腦中植入恐懼的觀念。看不見的激光的想法比執法武器本身更具效果，因為比槍更恐怖的就是中槍的想法了。<br />\n<br />\n如今看來，不論ZKZM-500激光槍效力的真假如何，從有關輿論發酵來判斷，中共可能已經成功製造了恐怖效果。<br />\n&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2018/07/09/a1382732.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fxtr%2Fb5%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2Fa1382732.html&d=Gwu7UGslcp1keCAvSO4gUNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=508e6f01\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com/xtr/b5/2018/07/09/a1382732.html</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T05:08:03.000Z","msg":"鬼佬有報過 .. 應該係真但係洩露左出黎 ... <br />\n三戰就係各大文明 Show off 既時間."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"你就鬼佬<br />\nSCMP嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5147685b26595675293ecb139e9c0d4e91a8f31","tid":771434,"uid":198943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:28:48.000Z","msg":"攞技電筒照死人<br />\n佢唔爆炸算你好命"},{"pid":"b44f3b7f7548983aa5ee986807fd3408460009bf","tid":771434,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:34:47.000Z","msg":"支那大媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461f06c8dce8a01d6dcf2288f4f41aee3968f253","tid":771434,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"taobao link pls <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b371be54618b1893074e2fac9c310110994b2044","tid":771434,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:39:43.000Z","msg":"睇嚟要買翻支粉紅迫擊砲防身"},{"pid":"24d20ada9cf090859dbd3b865605f66ba376b777","tid":771434,"uid":148600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:52:18.000Z","msg":"用鏡反射返去"},{"pid":"f8cdb1167248f414f6761f59b1eab14762163430","tid":771434,"uid":30186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T06:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e271a4f557f2bb36287ac2144cff87f42af4c0e3","tid":771434,"uid":185258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"屌，勁又點，咪又係對付平民"},{"pid":"4a61660867416b027f88a001892b64afe135fa12","tid":771434,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be49bd9fa4977f3966c2dcfd2fe4e940f87440c","tid":771434,"uid":35347,"like":1,"dislike"